Crear Ambiente
conda create --name Ambiente

Activar Ambiente
activate Ambiente

Instalar Tensorflow
conda install tensorflow

pip install keras

Instalar R
conda install r-essentials --yes

Instalar RStudio
conda install -c r rstudio --yes

Actualizar todos los paquetes
conda update --all


pip install nltk


pip install opencv-python
pip install numpy
pip install imutils
